  "text": "Similar torsion examples have been studied by other researchers although for square cross sections. [CITATION_1] obtained an open-walled frame-like structure which must be attributed to the coarse mesh used for the study. [CITATION_2] studied the same problem and found that with mesh refinement the optimized structure goes from being frame-like to being closed-walled -fully in agreement with the findings of the present paper.",
